column1: 3D Tree Barks on Dark Grey Background Pattern Wallpaper by IDIYA Ltd.
column3:
For nature lovers out there who would love to boost the green ambience of their homes with a stunning, nature-inspired interior wallpaper design, the 3D Tree Barks on Dark Grey Background Pattern Wallpaper by Idiya Ltd. is the perfect choice for you.
Introduce a nature-inspired design into your space with its 3D tree barks pattern on a dark grey background that will effortlessly cover your dull and cracked walls and incredibly enhance your beaut interior while giving your room a subtle and calming sage without becoming too overpowering.
This self-adhesive wallpaper is made from high-quality PVC material and comes in a vinyl texture, resulting in a more durable and smoother surface. It is lightweight and made of natural, environment-friendly and long-lasting materials, making sure that it will last on your walls for years. With its waterproof feature, you can install it even in your bathroom or kitchen area as well.
What’s more, this wallpaper is quick and easy to install, so you can do it yourself without the hassle of hiring any professional for help. It also doesn’t require any complex cleaning techniques — just wipe it when needed, and you’re all good.
Leave your friends and family impressed with an incredible wall decor upgrade on their next visit. Reinvent your old and dull walls with the 3D Tree Barks on Dark Grey Background Pattern Wallpaper by Idiya Ltd., and achieve that sleek and charming look you’ve always wanted — at an affordable cost.

A look that is both unique and sophisticated can be hard to find, but this wallpaper is good as gold. Cover your bare accented walls with the 3D Wood Effect With Red Accents Pattern Wallpaper by IDIYA Ltd. and leave your friends and family impressed with a striking wallpaper upgrade on their next visit.

column1: Alger Double Power Point with USB Charger
column3:
"The Alger Double Power Point With USB Charger works perfectly for multiple usage needs in your bach or home. Whether you want to charge a device, switch on the lights, or plug an appliance, you can do it all at once , thanks to this beaut. You are indeed hitting not just two but almost three birds with one stone when you opt for this product , all at an affordable cost. It is undoubtedly something you should take a squiz at.
This power point with USB charger comes with two (2) USB sockets, two (2) switches and two (2) 10A three-pole plat sockets. What’s more, it features a dimension of 115 mm x 74 mm and a thickness of 12 mm for the casing block and 1 mm for the faceplate. Its ratings are for 10A and 250 VAC. On top of that, this product is also SAA certified and follows Australia and New Zealand standards.
Its white design and the symmetrical output of all the features can add beauty and functionality to any part of your room. Note: Make sure that you choose the right location for this because it’s perfect for charging multiple devices at the same time, especially when your guests or buddies hang out in your house.
Your bach or home deserves a stunning makeover, and nothing can make your living room, entertainment room or even your bedroom more functional than the Alger Double Power Point With USB Charger. Get it today and leave your family and guests impressed with a stunning and functional upgrade on their next visit."

column1: Greyish-Blue Natural Granite Marble Pattern Wallpaper by IDIYA Ltd.
column3:
If you are looking to enhance your bach or home's old and dull walls, the Natural Greyish-blue Granite Marble Pattern Wallpaper by Idiya Ltd. is your best bet.

Whether you want to use it for your living room, dining area, home office, bedroom, or study area, this granite marble patterned wallpaper will instantly add a chic yet natural look to your space. Its classic greyish-blue colour combination makes it a perfect choice for your interior, which can also be used on almost all flat surfaces such as tables, counters, feature walls, and so on. 

This self-adhesive wallpaper is made from high-quality PVC material and comes in a vinyl texture, resulting in a more durable and smoother surface. It is lightweight and made of natural, environment-friendly and long-lasting materials, making sure that it will last on your walls for years. With its waterproof feature, you can install it even in your bathroom or kitchen area as well. 

What’s more, this wallpaper is quick and easy to install, so you can do it yourself without the hassle of hiring any professional for help. It also doesn't require any complex cleaning techniques  , just wipe it when needed, and you're all good.

Cover your plain accented walls with the Natural Greyish-blue Granite Marble Pattern Wallpaper by Idiya Ltd. and leave your friends and family impressed with a timeless wall decor upgrade on their next visit.

column1: IDIYA LABUAN Sofa Light Grey
column3: Assembly Video: https://youtu.be/0TUU2imx9c0 Let’s face it — your bach or home deserves the brightest and tightest glam. Let any part of your room be transformed aesthetically with this fantastic addition without spending too much. style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);"> style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">If you are tired of using your dull L-shaped sofa with ugly colours, you can’t go wrong with the Idiya Labuan Sofa in Light Grey. It will be the best choice for replacing your old and outdated furniture in no time. style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">This lovely piece of furniture features a rounded and soft design and looks throughout its overall body, resulting in a well-designed sofa, providing a vintage feel to any room it becomes part of. Meanwhile, it translates to a soft and comfortable sitting experience while still retaining a fashionable look and vintage inspiration. style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">Being made out of high-quality materials and smooth surface, you can expect that your and your guests’ sitting experience will be a highly comfortable and unique one, making it the perfect sofa for households with small kids in their family. The extended sitting cushion called chaise can be set up in any configuration the user desires (left or right side), making it a versatile and customisable product. Plus, both the sitting and back support cushions are filled with soft foam materials, resulting in a silky texture that is easy and gentle to one’s touch. style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">On top of that, the bottom space it creates due to its elevated base can be used to store your footwear if you want to relax your feet after a long day of heavy activities. Do note that this particular furniture is an L-Shape sofa, so it will have an extended seat cushion wherein you can use to place your legs on top to stretch them out. Likewise, it can be used as an extra seating space if needed. The cushions themselves are soft to the touch as well. style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">The clean and modern design of this furniture, along with its striking light grey colour closely resembling a grey-bluish hue, will surely be a welcome match to many vintages and modern home interiors of many bachs or homes nowadays. style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">Thanks to the high quality, durable materials used for construction, you can be sure that every money spent on this elegant sofa will be an overall worthwhile purchase as it will last you for many years upon purchase and with regular use — all at an affordable cost. What’s more, this solid and sturdy sofa can easily handle large amounts of weight when used. style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">Your bach or home deserves a stunning makeover, and nothing can revamp your room more than the Idiya Labuan Light Grey Sofa. Get it today and leave your family and guests impressed with a stunning and functional furniture upgrade on their next visit.

A solid seater sofa that can also double as an extra bed, the Idiya Zheng Zhou with Patch Design Sofa Bed is a must-have for many baches or homes as its dual-purpose nature can provide additional sleeping spaces for guests and owners alike. Made from high standard quality materials, the whole sofa bed's cover fabric features a unique-looking patch design in specific parts of the entire sofa. Those said patches have a different colour tone, providing a great contrast to the dark base colour used for the majority of the sofa body. And as its name suggests, this well-designed piece of furniture can be used as a full sofa bed wherein one to two adults can sleep on it when its back supports are fully deployed , all at an affordable cost. This feature is really useful for bach or homeowners who need an extra bed space for their guests or if their own bed isn't available for use. What's more, thanks to the high-quality, durable materials used for construction, you can be sure that every money spent on this elegant sofa bed will be an overall worthwhile purchase as it will last you for many years upon purchase and with regular use. Your bach or home deserves a stunning makeover, and nothing can revamp your room more than the Idiya Zheng Zhou Sofa Bed with Patch Design. column1: IKEA ENHET Wall FR W Shelves Anthracite 60X30X75 cm
column3: Product description This open wall frame with 2 shelves gives a good overview and easy access to jars, bottles and things often used. You can use this open solution to create your own personal style at home. Display the things you love or why not emphasise a theme or colour? Can be used to create a break in a row of closed cabinets for an airier feel in the room. Slot hooks into the grooves on the sides of the frame to hang towels or containers. No drilling in walls necessary. Sold separately. Make the most of the space by attaching ENHET rail for hooks to the frame or shelves to hang hooks with containers, sold separately. Add ENHET hanging shelf insert or swivel shelf to create even more storage possibilities, sold separately. The unique wedge dowels make assembly easy and the fittings are nearly invisible. Why not go for a perfect mix of open and closed storage? Put often-used items in the open ENHET frames and hide things that often get cluttered in closed ENHET cabinets. Powder coated and galvanised steel withstands many years of use in environments exposed to water, splashes and humidity. 10 year guarantee. Read about the terms in the guarantee brochure. column1: IKEA Hallbar Bin with Lid Light Grey 22 L
column3: HÅLLBAR bins are designed to meet different waste sorting needs. This bin is perfect for sorting things like cardboard, plastic, paper, bottles, glass, tin cans, envelopes and advertising mail.HÅLLBAR bins are stackable to save space. Place same-size bins on top of each other or place smaller bins on top of the larger ones. It is easy to access the bin even when stacked thanks to the included lid. It is hinged and can be opened in two ways. A lid is included to hide your waste. It’s removeable for easy cleaning or if you prefer to keep your bin open. The bins can be placed freestanding anywhere in your home or integrated in a cabinet or drawer. The included sticker can be attached to the bin to mark what you are sorting. Draw or write on the sticker to make it clear what goes in the bin. By mounting HÅLLBAR pull out frame for waste sorting bins in a cabinet or HÅLLBAR support frame for waste sorting bins in MAXIMERA high drawer, the bins stay in place, and you get good access and overview. In the kitchen, mount your waste sorting as close to the sink as possible since this is where most waste is produced and to avoid spills. The bin is designed with rounded corners to make it easier to clean. The folding handle makes it easy to carry the bin with you to the waste station. A ring on the top edge of the bin hides the waste bag and keeps it in place. It’s removable either for easy cleaning or if not being used. If you are going to sort dry waste, you can complete with AJÖSS waste sorting bag 22l to avoid carrying the entire bin with you when it is time to empty it. column1: IKEA Maximera Drawer, Low, White, 60X60 cm
column3:
Yes, it's possible to fall in love with a drawer! This one pulls out all the way for a good overview and can be kept organized with the interiors of your choice. And the best part? It closes quietly! You can view and access what's inside, as the drawer can be pulled out all the way.

The smooth-running drawer is equipped with a drawer stop and is self-closing the last few centimeters. The drawer closes slowly, quietly and softly thanks to the built-in dampers.

You can create more storage with inner drawers, either inside a higher drawer or behind the door. To stay organized and for efficient use of space, MAXIMERA drawers may be completed with VARIERA organizer's like the cutlery tray, utensil tray or plate holder.

column3: Key features - Made of tempered glass, which makes the side plate extra resistant to impact and durable. Designer thoughts "The challenge when I designed OFTAST was to combine good function with a very low price. Designer Henrik Preutz about OFTAST

column3:
product description & measurements
Polypropylene plastic.

Key features
- A good set of basic food containers for everything from ham, cheese etc. to leftovers and individual food portions.
- Several empty food containers can be stacked inside one another to save space in your cabinets.
- Reduce food waste by storing your leftovers in a food container and reheating for another meal.
- The transparent jar makes it easy to find what you are looking for, regardless of where it is placed.
- Several food containers can be stacked on top of one another to save space in fridge and freezer.

good to know

Freezer-safe.
Dishwasher-safe.

  • Floor decking makes it easy to refresh your terrace or balcony.

column1: IKEA STACKHOLMEN Stool, Outdoor Light Brown Stained 48X35X43 cm
column3: Product description The frame of the stool is made of acacia, a hardwood that is naturally durable and sturdy thanks to the high density of its wood fibers. The stool is easy to move around on your balcony or terrace and place where you feel like sitting. Plastic feet protect the furniture when in contact with a moist surface. For added durability and so you can enjoy the natural expression of the wood, the furniture has been pre-treated with several layers of semi-transparent wood stain. Please refer to packaging label for country of origin This stool has been tested for home use and meets the requirements for durability and safety, set forth in the following standards: EN 581. For increased stability, re-tighten the screws about two weeks after assembly and when necessary. Only recommended for outdoor use. column1: Ikea PAX wardrobe frame 75x58x201cm, white stained oak effect
column3:
Do you dream of a beautiful wardrobe for your bedroom? Here´s the solution for you! Start with frames, after that add KOMPLEMENT series that stores all your clothes, shoes and accessories. In the end, just personalise it by adding your favourite doors. class="describe-text-p" data-v-6dc1bda6="" style="margin-bottom: 1.875rem; font-family: "Noto Ikea Latin", "Noto Sans", Roboto, "Open Sans", -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: none; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); word-spacing: 1px;">If you want to organise inside you can complement with interior organisers from the KOMPLEMENT series. class="describe-text-p" data-v-6dc1bda6="" style="margin-bottom: 1.875rem; font-family: "Noto Ikea Latin", "Noto Sans", Roboto, "Open Sans", -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: none; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); word-spacing: 1px;">Adjustable feet make it possible to compensate any irregularities in the floor. class="describe-text-p" data-v-6dc1bda6="" style="margin-bottom: 1.875rem; font-family: "Noto Ikea Latin", "Noto Sans", Roboto, "Open Sans", -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: none; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); word-spacing: 1px;">Please refer to packaging label for country of origin class="describe-text-p" data-v-6dc1bda6="" style="margin-bottom: 1.875rem; font-family: "Noto Ikea Latin", "Noto Sans", Roboto, "Open Sans", -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: none; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); word-spacing: 1px;">This furniture must be fixed to the wall with the enclosed wall fastener. class="describe-text-p" data-v-6dc1bda6="" style="margin-bottom: 1.875rem; font-family: "Noto Ikea Latin", "Noto Sans", Roboto, "Open Sans", -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: none; padding: 0px; color: rgb(72, 72, 72); word-spacing: 1px;">Different wall materials require different types of fixing devices. column3:
Sofa comfort when you dine? Believe it! Soft padding, zig-zag spring bottom and great support for back and arms make this chair all about comfort. column1: KANSAS Black Chair x 2pcs
column3:
MODERN INDUSTRIAL STYLE – A perfect seat for the dining room, kitchen, office, patio or restaurant cafe.
DURABLE CONSTRUCTION – Heavy duty Steel makes up the frame. The modern chair features a scratch-resistant, powder-coated finish and an X-brace for added support and stability
SPACE SAVING DESIGN – A practical seating solution, stackable design allows for convenient and space-saving storage options, while its rubber feet prevent scratching, marking and slipping.
INDOOR / OUTDOOR USE – Resistant to water, these can be used both indoors and under cover outdoors.
MEASUREMENTS:

Description
The Idiya Keelung Slat queen size bed frame has a clean and sleek design. This high bed frame will glam up your bedroom with decors of any style or colour. The bed frame is made of solid pine wood that gives you a long-lasting damage-free experience.  You won’t be needing a box spring as the bed slats provide reliable support for the mattress to stay propped up. The noise-free design will ensure you have the ultimate sleeping comfort.  This bed frame comes in 2 packages. All the tools, parts and instructions are included for stress-free assembly. The assembly instructions will be given along with the packages. 
Care
Wipe clean using a damp cloth and a mild cleaner Wipe dry with a clean cloth

The top of the table features a full 4cm layer of high-density foam covered in luxurious PVC synthetic leather. PVC leather is oil and water-proof. This massage table is expertly crafted with a sturdy hardwood frame and double tension knobs on each leg for added stability. The table support cables utilize the same quality steel used in automobile brake construction, making for a strong table that can support up to 200kgs. style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.5em; padding: 0px; font-family: Lato, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);">Overall dimensions for the folded table are 91cm long x 17cm wide x 61cm high.
